| 00_Central_Core | Index_MOC, Learning_Path, Concept_Connections, Quick_Snippets |
| 10_Universal_Laws | Variables, Operators, String |
| 20_Logic_Flow | Conditionals, Loops, Error_Handling, Testing, Logging, Async |
| 30_Data_Vault | Lists, Dictionaries, Sets |
